730
00:29:57,580 --> 00:30:00,600
 Sloboda je u tebi.

731
00:30:00,600 --> 00:30:04,880
 Da sam barem iskrena pred tobom,

732
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:08,100
 možda bih tada imala hrabrosti

733
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:11,400
 biti iskrena i sa samom sobom.

734
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:13,260
 Aamen.

